      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<big><b>מגלחין ומביאין קרבן טומאה",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 57a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "180px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "וקרבן טהרה ואומר",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 57a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "כו</b></big>. לאו דוקא נקט ואומר אלא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 57a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "זה יקרב לשם מי שהוא וזה יקרב",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 57a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לשם מי שהוא.",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 57a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
